{"tid":33321,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"麻友反共 勁過班狗吠90 00 後多多聲","createTime":"2016-12-10T17:25:32.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-12T00:58:30.000Z","uid":3806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f90ce72a5751d3c9d683ece1e626c67c810927b2","tid":33321,"uid":3806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T17:25:32.000Z","msg":"【中國不歡迎你】AKB48上海騷遭反日人士抗議 粉絲反擊 搶中國國旗丟入垃圾桶 <br />\n<br />\n日本女子偶像組合AKB48派出三名成員渡邊麻友、川本紗矢同伊豆田莉奈現身上海舉行嘅活動，宣佈組合嚟緊喺中國嘅發展大計。 <br />\n<br />\n現場除咗唔少AKB嘅國內粉絲，仲有一班愛國人士踩場，佢哋手執「萬眾一心 愛我中華 抵制日韓」嘅字句，仲有人拎住AKB同日本首相安倍晉三嘅合照，以及AKB為日本自衞隊拍攝嘅宣傳海報。現場嘅抗議人士話，「一二．九」抗日救亡運動紀念日啱啱過咗，南京大屠殺紀念日又即將來臨，偏偏喺呢個時候有對中日關係有負面影響嘅偶像團體嚟到大陸，「實在令人難以接受」。 <br />\n<br />\n據報道指，一眾反日抗議人士令在現嘅AKB支持者非常不滿，fans激動得扯下橫額，兼用日語罵爆，更將抗議者手中嘅大陸國旗丟入垃圾桶。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161210/large/1481363913_04d9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161210%2Flarge%2F1481363913_04d9.jpg&h=aecbc48b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161210/large/1481363896_516f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161210%2Flarge%2F1481363896_516f.jpg&h=7e9a5dda&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161210/large/1481363897_aedb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161210%2Flarge%2F1481363897_aedb.jpg&h=037a6bc1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n反日抗議人士令到現場嘅AKB支持者非常不滿，展開衝突。 <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161210/large/1481363898_214f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161210%2Flarge%2F1481363898_214f.jpg&h=83b16c6f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n仲有人將中國國旗丟入垃圾桶。"},{"pid":"841d38ff03b2a6731863a702981b11d0395468af","tid":33321,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T17:27:19.000Z","msg":"Ching 做乜開咁多個post ？"},{"pid":"fc8def10de9d9881b88b7ed9ab1bfc77f951b9c4","tid":33321,"uid":3806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T17:30:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Ching 做乜開咁多個post ？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n琴日掛住打機無開到<br />\n今日補番"},{"pid":"bb91081a8cca3952a6129f2fa3832b450a677461","tid":33321,"uid":19195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T17:59:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Ching 做乜開咁多個post ？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n琴日掛住打機無開到<br />\n今日補番</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdecf710529b9f0292bc08d91a8b54d88fa76592","tid":33321,"uid":3806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T18:13:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Ching 做乜開咁多個post ？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n琴日掛住打機無開到<br />\n今日補番</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真定假野來"},{"pid":"35d34a31e9471af138d626d80da74c533ce4849f","tid":33321,"uid":19195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T18:33:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Ching 做乜開咁多個post ？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n琴日掛住打機無開到<br />\n今日補番</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真定假野來</blockquote><br />\nChing 冇人會好似你咁好地地扮我 =.="},{"pid":"7ea4e6a5502b4620b2fee273d3986230d8c8a2bc","tid":33321,"uid":3806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T02:03:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真定假野來</blockquote><br />\nChing 冇人會好似你咁好地地扮我 =.=</blockquote><br />\n😂"},{"pid":"3d1575e5f22db8a69b18383b4a74b65e780ea390","tid":33321,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite